"title": "6689: mercy, of Jesus Christ",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6689",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Jesus Christ displays the same attitude of grace and mercy towards men and women as his Father does.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is merciful</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:16-Luke4:21\">LUK 4:16–4:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:2\">ISA 61:1–61:2</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:12-John15:13\">JHN 15:12–15:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:9\">2CO 8:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:14\">2CO 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:7\">EPH 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:1\">PHP 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:16\">1TI 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:18\">2TI 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:1\">2TI 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:21\">JUD 1:21</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's concern for people in need</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:36\">MAT 9:36</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:34\">MRK 6:34</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:14\">MAT 14:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:32\">MAT 15:32</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:2\">MRK 8:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:37\">MAT 23:37</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:34\">LUK 13:34</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's response to appeals for mercy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:30-Matt20:34\">MAT 20:30–20:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:2-Matt8:3\">MAT 8:2–8:3</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:39-Mark1:40\">MRK 1:39–1:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:12-Luke5:13\">LUK 5:12–5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:5-Matt8:13\">MAT 8:5–8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:18-Matt9:30\">MAT 9:18–9:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:22\">MAT 15:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:14-Matt17:18\">MAT 17:14–17:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:6\">JHN 11:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:8-2Cor12:9\">2CO 12:8–12:9</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's mercy in response to judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:47\">JHN 12:47</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ as high priest</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:17-Heb2:18\">HEB 2:17–2:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:15\">HEB 4:15</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's mercy is shown in his actions</h2>\n<h3>In salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:2\">EPH 5:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:10\">LUK 19:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:20\">GAL 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25\">EPH 5:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:14-1Tim1:16\">1TI 1:14–1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:4-Titus3:7\">TIT 3:4–3:7</a></p>\n<h3>In forgiveness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:34\">LUK 23:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:10\">MRK 2:10</a></p>\n<h3>In blessing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:13-Mark10:16\">MRK 10:13–10:16</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:13-Matt19:15\">MAT 19:13–19:15</a></p>",
